{"tid":327600,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投]你地睇故鍾意睇書面文定口語文？","createTime":"2017-07-19T01:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T04:41:49.000Z","uid":33154,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"481d252e31bc91209645a53d3cef736b4e44f3f4","tid":327600,"uid":33154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:24:29.000Z","msg":"口語文姐係<br />\n「阿傑約咗我去食譚仔」<br />\n書面文姐係<br />\n「阿傑約了我去吃譚仔」<br />\n<br />\n個人而言<br />\n我係鍾意睇書面文既故多d<br />\n總係覺得用書面語<br />\n情感表達可以細膩d<br />\n同埋個環境描述可以立體d<br />\n唯一我覺得用口語文好d既<br />\n就剩係得類似「一人一個恐怖經歷」呢d極細故咁<br />\n但整體黎講我都係覺得書面文好睇d<br />\n<br />\n但我呢排追post<br />\n見到有好多人都唔同諗法<br />\n甚至有d人見到書面文<br />\n會留言屌佢大陸feel<br />\n要樓主打返口語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足點睇？<br />\n不如一齊討論下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   - 書面文<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  - 口語文"},{"pid":"ce9af421e53c75c0f1684b2ed074a78fc2cdc242","tid":327600,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"書面語 口語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a157769425c4b704aa450836133f86325c2db549","tid":327600,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:27:41.000Z","msg":"書面語都會自己心入面轉返口語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以無咩野<br />\n不過都係鍾意睇口語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efa0e115cdd0a7f58acb6acac425e84fe480db7","tid":327600,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci